bbcode_enabled = true
bbcode_text = "Located in the bottom panel are the warnings.

Warnings are categorised as either [color=#E43B44]\"danger\"[/color] or [color=#FEE761]\"caution\"[/color] based on if they exceed any of the safety limits.

The ping button allows you to send a notification to the truck driver so that they can respond accordingly. [color=#181425]Note that the act of actually sending the ping has been left unimplemented.[/color]

The view limits button allows you to see both the caution limits and the safe limits. If a value is within the caution limits then it will be marked as [color=#63C74D]safe[/color] and so no warning will be displayed. However, if it is outside the caution limits then it will be either marked as [color=#FEE761]caution[/color] or as [color=#E43B44]danger[/color]. This is determined by if it also falls outside the safe limits (in which it will be marked as [color=#E43B44]danger[/color])."
text = "Located in the bottom panel are the warnings.

